title: Dark Cloud
content:
Can anyone identify this font? I think it make be a custom font made by the company, But it doesn't hurt to ask.   
 ![Dark Cloud Logo](http://web.archive.org/web/20141009175045im_/http:/www.typophile.com/forums/messages/83/7099.jpg)
author: azel

comments.content: It sure looks hand-done to me; if it is, however, I'm disappointed that the two Ds are identical.
Do you know of any fonts that may look a bit like this font? Or even tell me what kind of style it is?
